description:
Brooke and Danielle are talking SPRING BREAK!!  The gals share their funniest (and wildest) spring break stories, best places to shop for spring break attire + bathing suits, and how to have the best time possible.  Brooke and Danielle also catch up on their weekends and talk about their upcoming trip to Mexico!  Cheers to spring break!  Be sure to tag @galsonthegopodcast in your listening selfies/stories!
